{"tid":1858783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「醫療不如台日，卻沒有確診病例」: 這個國家不得了　","createTime":"2020-02-03T02:06:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T07:09:12.000Z","uid":184679,"like":647,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":110,"replies":[{"pid":"1dd34b331a27c06a4971e7db1eee42db721c642c","tid":1858783,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T02:06:07.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情越演越烈，各國祭出各種防疫手段希望阻擋病毒入侵。台灣駐日代表謝長廷2日在臉書上表示，北韓是最早拒絕中國旅客進入的國家，即使醫療水準不如台日，但決策迅速，所以短期內能控制疫情不擴大。<br />\n<br />\n謝長廷提到，在春節前1月22日，北韓就封閉中韓邊境，拒絕中國觀光客入境，連帶其他外國觀光客也禁止，也因此徹底阻斷病毒流入的可能性，所以北韓迄今沒有新型肺炎的確診病例。而俄羅斯也取消許多直航中國的航班，鄰近中國的城鎮，據報載都主動關閉交流往來。所以俄羅斯一直到1月31日才有2個確診病例，而且都是中國籍，目前更加強切斷中俄邊境的交通聯結。<br />\n<br />\n謝長廷分析，這2個國家都是中國的好朋友，尤其北韓對中國的依賴很深，即使醫療水準不如台日，但決策迅速，防疫如打戰，保護自己國人為優先，不講客氣也不講人情，所以短期內能控制疫情不擴大。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.storm.mg/article/2247061\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.storm.mg%2Farticle%2F2247061&d=aEshCX%2BOVPgV%2F8nDcbq7VwomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=e645075a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.storm.mg/article/2247061</a>"},{"pid":"2bf4aa8a9ed25141e6322eb9491fff222df854a6","tid":1858783,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T02:06:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e5e04eb5df755b95540b46f6c8ef43f1feadbf7","tid":1858783,"uid":74896,"like":180,"dislike":2,"score":178,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T02:07:30.000Z","msg":"同支那熟，知內情"},{"pid":"2068dd7c38cc322474082dcd9d84d643449f356c","tid":1858783,"uid":184679,"like":222,"dislike":2,"score":220,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T02:07:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/HXpKwTs4hX0F02pzIgOJ-E5EPSfP-OplV_GeXM0gEAHO-hXq5hbPjqwi_ilTiPwkcLyhnwXuDIQhnG_11hxPxA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2FHXpKwTs4hX0F02pzIgOJ-E5EPSfP-OplV_GeXM0gEAHO-hXq5hbPjqwi_ilTiPwkcLyhnwXuDIQhnG_11hxPxA&h=49bb2ab5&s={SIZE}\" />